scene_description: A crow is flying towards a tree branch with a piece of food in its beak under a blue sky.
A fox looks up at a crow sitting on a tree branch, which is holding a piece of bread in its beak.
A crow sits on a tree branch with a piece of food in its beak, while a fox looks up at the crow, seemingly trying to trick it into dropping the food.
A crow perched on a tree branch is shown dropping a piece of food from its open beak.
A crow on a tree branch is dropping a piece of food from its beak towards a fox looking up from below.
A vibrant orange fox is captured in mid-stride, running along a dirt path next to a tree and lush green grass under a clear blue sky.
